casebody.data:
Second Department,

June, 1937.

(June 7, 1937.) Bjarne Bensen, Respondent, v. Frederick W. Kristeller and Ora Kristeller, Appellants.

Motion for reargument denied, without costs. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Stay granted until the granting or final refusal by the Court of Appeals of leave to appeal. Present —. Lazansky, P. J., Hagarty, Davis, Johnston and Close, JJ.
